headline: AmEx, Chase, Capital One: Which has the best travel credit card?
summary: Premium travel card fees are in focus after the Chase (JPM) Sapphire Reserve credit card's annual fee recently increased to $795, while American Express (AXP) refreshed its AmEx Platinum card. Yahoo Finance Personal Finance Reporter Ben Walker joins Mind Your Money host Allie Canal to discuss whether the new AmEx Platinum benefits are worth the hefty fees, and how the card compares to the Chase Sapphire Reserve and the Capital One (COF) Venture X card.
